Package tdam

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    InputHandler
    Interface for writing to and reading from an input buffer.
    OutputHandler
    Interface for providing a list of units matching a given name.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Association
    Class for an association in the network.
    InputHandlerAbstract
    Abstract class for writing to and reading from an input buffer.
    InputHandlerUDP
    Class for writing to and reading from an input buffer using the UDP protocol.
    Network
    Class for holding the network of units and associations.
    OutputHandlerAbstract
    Abstract class for providing a list of units containing a given name as a first word in their data pattern.
    OutputHandlerUDP
    Class for providing a list of units containing the given name as a first word in their data pattern and sending this list on request over a UDP connection.
    Simulation
    Class for a running TDAM simulation.
    Unit
    Class for a unit in the network.
    XMLReader
    Class for reading a network state of TDAM from an XML file.
    XMLWriter
    Class for writing a network state of TDAM to an XML file.
